text: I arrived in the afternoon, just after the lunch hour. It wasn't too crowded at that time, although some groups started arriving as I was about to leave. I really love the ambiance; the white decor creates a minimalist and tidy atmosphere. There are plenty of Instagram-worthy spots if you enjoy taking pictures. I highly recommend trying their signature drink—it tastes great!

Free wall plugs, no wifi , decent pasta food with matcha drink, the mushroom soup with the garlic bread is delicious , would advice the staffs to clear the plates since the flies might keep flying around.. ambience is nice, next to cafe is the kart racing.
Nice environment. Not much food option if you don’t take beef.

After racing, we feel so hungry. So we had the Lalapot set, 2 refreshing drinks and Tiramisu. The lalapot was so berbaloi for 2, I think can feed more people. Everything was fresh. Even the drinks are very good and the tiramisu is actually very good! The staff is friendly and helpful too!
An interesting, quiet and cozy cafe..suitable for family sessions..friendly staff..can relax after playing go-kart..appetizing steamboat dishes, fresh seafood..desserts are also delicious.
